    "description": "Shree Cement Ventures Solutions is actively seeking a talented and motivated Process Engineer to join our dynamic team in Amritsar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Shree Cement Ventures Solutions:\nShree Cement Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in TPM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shree Cement Ventures Solutions!",
